metadata.name: FATHER'S TIME
metadata.description:
I made this photo in Kyiv, Ukraine. The fisherman in the boat is the father of this kid. Kid all the time where asking to go in the boat with his father, but the boat was super tiny, just to fit father there. So this fisherman told his kid that he needs his help on the bank. That is why this boy stands on a bank with his fishing rod. 
	It reminds me my time, when I was asking to go on a fishing with my dad, just to spend time with him, despite I hate fishing...
